      "text": "そうね、学校が終わったら\n最近はすぐに東京に戻らないといけなかったし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ after school‚\nwe usually had to head back to Tokyo right away.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4666659512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
